# 暖流人心 GitHub Pages — .gitignore
# 紀律：紅線 3 守住（依 Atlas 法規軸覆核 5/08 + 閘門 13 redact 鐵律）

# === 紅線 3：API key / token / secrets 絕不 commit ===
.env
.env.*
*.env
meta_credentials.env
secrets.json
*.secret
*.token
*.key
*.pem
*.crt
*.cert
credentials.json
service-account*.json
*api_key*
*ANTHROPIC*
*OPENAI*
*GITHUB_TOKEN*
*META_*TOKEN*
*LINE_*TOKEN*
*THREADS_*TOKEN*

# === Age 加密檔案不 commit（雙雲備份用，不上 GitHub）===
*.age

# === 個案資料絕不 commit（紅線 1 + 個資法 + 業倫理）===
個案*
case_*
client_*
patient_*
治療紀錄*
*個資*

# === Plaud 錄音原始檔不 commit（含可能個案聲音）===
Inbox/Plaud錄音/
*.plaud
*.wav
*.mp3
*.m4a

# === Jekyll 編譯產出 ===
_site/
.jekyll-cache/
.jekyll-metadata
.bundle/
vendor/

# === Sass 編譯快取 ===
.sass-cache/
*.css.map

# === Node ===
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*

# === Python ===
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/

# === Editor / OS ===
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.tmp
*.bak

# === 測試 / 草稿 ===
draft/
test/
sandbox/
TEST_*

# === 資料 / 分析 ===
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.db
*.sqlite

# === 大檔案（GitHub 100MB 限制）===
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.7z
*.dmg
*.iso

# === 圖檔（如過大）===
*.psd
*.ai

# === 影片 ===
*.mp4
*.mov
*.avi
*.mkv

# === Logs ===
*.log
logs/
